2015-04-24 18-00-00:
	Title: New OpenRA release out now! This is not a drill!
	Author: Oliver Brakmann
	Content: We are thrilled to announce the Spring release of OpenRA!\n\nThis release, almost six months in the making, is one of our biggest yet: it contains countless new features, bug fixes and improvements. Sandworms and Carryalls for Dune 2000 and playable Countries in Red Alert are the most visible enhancements, but there is lots more to discover!\n\nCheck out http://openra.net for the full announcement and http://changelog.openra.net for the complete changelog.\n\nEnjoy and have a lot of fun! Thank you!
